# Whistle conventions

- Ship a **fan prediction product**, not a proof explorer or sportsbook clone.
- Keep TxLINE as the primary live data source; demo fixtures only when credentials are absent.
- Put score→outcome math in `@whistle/shared` and reuse it from API/keeper/UI.
- Parimutuel pools; lock stakes when a match goes live; void+refund on cancel/postpone.
- Do not commit secrets (`.env`, `wallet.json`, API tokens).
- Prefer updating `docs/TECH.md` when changing settlement or TxLINE integration.
